      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every service schedule. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for an adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
