    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a concours-level example of the naturally aspirated S65 V8 era. The 4.0L powerplant features eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, delivering linear power through a precision-calibrated 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, featuring the weight-saving carbon fiber roof panel for a lower center of gravity. Equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M-Variable Differential Lock, the vehicle offers surgical turn-in and exceptional lateral grip. Mechanically pristine with a documented service history, this specimen represents the pinnacle of hydraulic steering feedback and atmospheric induction.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
