      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presenting in absolute showroom condition. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks or stone chips, having been professionally ceramic coated and stored in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no signs of bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive cruise control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a meticulous service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians. It drives with the same precision and tightness as the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved example for the most discerning collector.",
